==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sibilate
<hw>Sib"i*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>To
pronounce with a hissing sound, like that of the letter <it>s</it>; to
mark with a character indicating such pronunciation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sibilation</ent>⟦br⟧
